<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. مَنْ أَطْلَعَ البَدْرَا ... عَلَى جَبِينِكَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَأَوْدَعَ السِّحْرَا ... بَيْنَ جُفُونِكَ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَرَوَّعَ السُّمْرَا ... بِفَرْطِ لِينِكَ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يَا لَكَ مِنْ قَدِّ ... مَهْمَا تَأَوَّدْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَهْدَى إِلَى الزَّهْرِ ... خَداً مُوَّرَّدْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>قُمْ فَاقْتَدِحِ زَنْدَا ... مِنَ العُقَارِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>قَدْ قُلِّدَتْ عِقْدَا ... مِنَ الدَّرَارِي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَأُلْبِسَتْ بُرْدَا ... مِنَ النُّضَارِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَاشْرَبْ عَلَى وَرْدِ ... عَلْيَا مُحَمَّدْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>نَاهِيكَ مِنْ سِرِّ ... وَطِيبِ مَوْرِدْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>النَّصْرُ يَلْتَاحُ ... عَلَى عُلاهُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>الزَّهْرُ يَرْتَاحُ ... إِلَى نَدَاهُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>مَا الصُّبْحُ وَضَّاحُ ... لَوْلا سُرَاهُ ... فَالْبِسْ مِنَ المَجْدِ ... بُرْدَاً مُعَضَّدْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَانْظُمْ مِنَ الشِّعْرِ ... دُرَّا مُنَضَّدْ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>للهِ مَا أَعْلَى ... فِي كُلِّ حَالِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>ملك قد اسْتَوْلَى ... عَلَى الكَمَالِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>مَقَلَّدَاً نَصْلا ... مِنَ الجَّلالِ ...<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>